In amid of all tensions b/w India & Pakistan 

Step back and Listen this song ... Then decide that 

- Should we be fighting with each other or stay together and fight with Terrorism #Murdabad
- Should we be competing with each other or stay together and compete with this whole World 

Jai Hind ... Hindustan Zindabad... Pakistan Jindabad too!
Also, Khalsa Zindabad Khalsa Zindabad ... Punjabi's (from both nations) Zindabad ... other religion Zindabad

But => Khalistan ... no we don't want ... I am an Indian ... I have my country which is called India ...

Thanks,
Harry Manchanda, From India (I wish I could say From India - that was together before 1947)
